      <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
         <head>Biographical History</head>
         
      <p>Gladys Brierly Ashour (1907?-2000) was an American author of children's books and stories.</p></bioghist>
      
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
         <p>The <emph render="bold">Gladys Brierly Ashour Typescripts</emph> consists of six typescripts of Ashour's children's stories.  Titles are given 
		 in full in the inventory below.  At least one was explicitly submitted as a picture book, but the manuscripts do not include 
		 any illustrations, only text.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      
      <arrangement encodinganalog="351$a">
